OL,5,G0255 Citizen Smith
OL,6,     FThe Weekend: Ken falls in love
OL,7,     Fwith the girlfriend of one of
OL,8,     FWolfie's prison-bound friends and
OL,9,     Farranges to take her away for the
OL,10,     Fweekend, but Wolfie tags along to
OL,11,     Fkeep an eye on things.
OL,12,G0330 Citizen Smith
OL,13,     FThe Hostage: Following a
OL,14,     Fby-election humiliation in which
OL,15,     Fhe gained a mere 6 votes, Wolfie
OL,16,     Fplans to kidnap the Conservative
OL,17,     Fwho beat him. There's nothing as
OL,18,     Fbad as democracy!
