OL,5,G0400 Citizen Smith
OL,6,     FThe Path of True Love: When a
OL,7,     Fcustomer starts chatting up
OL,8,     FShirley in the shop, she decides
OL,9,     Fto move on from Wolfie - which
OL,10,     Fmeans the fearless leader may have
OL,11,     Fto move out of her spare room.
OL,12,G0430 Citizen Smith
OL,13,     FBut Is It Art?: Wolfie is on the
OL,14,     Flookout for any money-making
OL,15,     Fopportunity he can find. When
OL,16,     FKen's attention is firmly taken up
OL,17,     Fby pavement art, Citizen Smith may
OL,18,     Fhave found his answer.
